Package: svgtools
Type: Package
Title: Manipulate SVG template files of diagrams.
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2019-04-03
Authors@R:
  c(person("Konrad","Oberwimmer",email="konrad.oberwimmer@iqs.gv.at",role=c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Christian","Wimmer",role="aut"),
    person("Michael","Bruneforth",role="ctb"))
Description: This package takes SVG-format files and manipulates named elements (that is, elements with tag 'id' in the XML-representation).
    The main goal is to rescale and reposition bar segments, lines, symbols and texts to accurately represent coefficients in diagrams for which only uninformative templates exist.
